{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0003", "text": "你在懷舊 我也懂 還稱讚我夠上進", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 0, 2, 5, 5, 9, 0, 3, 4, 5, 4, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "zoi6", "waai4", "gau6", "ngo5", "jaa5", "dung2", "waan4", "cing1", "zaan3", "ngo5", "gau3", "zeon3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懷舊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "稱讚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "進", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "必殺技", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1247", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0004", "text": "但可惜那時你都不相信", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 9, 3, 5, 0, 5, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "ho2", "sik1", "naa5", "si4", "nei5", "dou1", "bat1", "seon3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可惜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "相信", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "必殺技", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1247", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0005", "text": "我道行都低估了你 我以爲 撐得起", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 0, 3, 3, 9, 5, 5, 5, 5, 3, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "dou6", "hang4", "dou1", "dai1", "gu2", "liu5", "nei5", "ngo5", "ji5", "caang1", "dak1", "hei2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "道行", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低估", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "以爲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撐", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "起", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "必殺技", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1247", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0006", "text": "一句爲什麼不找找你", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 2, 3, 3, 9, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jat1", "geoi3", "sam6", "mo1", "bat1", "zaau2", "zaau2", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "一句", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "必殺技", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1247", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
